342
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:35,330
[ Crash ]

343
00:18:40,170 --> 00:18:47,710
[ Laughter ]

344
00:18:48,110 --> 00:18:48,710
Wow.

345
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:51,350
That did not go
as well as I expected.

346
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:53,890
I can't believe
they're laughing at us!

347
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:56,050
Was it that bad?

348
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:59,670
Back on stage, girls!
It's time for the awards!

349
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:01,930
Back on stage?
No.

350
00:19:02,330 --> 00:19:04,180
They'll just laugh
some more!

351
00:19:04,390 --> 00:19:06,240
Yeah.
What's the point?

352
