00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:04,630
And instead of forcing ourselves

390
00:21:04,670 --> 00:21:06,710
To do something
that's not meant for us...

391
00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:08,530
yes? Yes?

392
00:21:08,810 --> 00:21:11,530
