our true talent.

393
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:13,260
And that is?

394
00:21:14,010 --> 00:21:15,450
Comedy!
Comedy!
Comedy!

395
00:21:18,010 --> 00:21:19,940
Apple Bloom,
you did it!

396
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:21,850
All:
did you see our award?

